Please optimize this matrix multiplication function for better cache locality:

```cpp

    void matrix_multiply(double* A, double* B, double* C, int n) {
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
                C[i*n + j] = 0;
                for (int k = 0; k < n; k++) {
                    C[i*n + j] += A[i*n + k] * B[k*n + j];
                }
            }
        }
    }

